title: [Gyldemar Forest, Crooked Path]
description: The path twists and bends around several large oaks.  Green grass struggles for light and space amongst the trees.  A few fallen branches have formed a home for a badger family.
The path twists and bends wildly in the night around several large oaks.  Green grass struggles for space amongst the trees.  A few fallen branches have formed a home for a badger family.
